&lt;p&gt;The Microbiology Department is looking to recruit Bank staff to help with Data entry onto our Laboratory information management system (WinPath Enterprise). The successful candidate will be based at St Richards Hospital, Chichester, working alongside Medical laboratory Assistants and another Band 4 Associate Practitioner, supporting the Specialist Biomedical Scientists and reporting to the Microbiology Head Biomedical Scientist. The successful individuals will be expected to possess previous experience of data entry and to have worked in a Clinical Microbiology Laboratory.&lt;/p&gt;
